header.info: A very active sheep with cute green horns.[br][br]Gus plays sounds, has many of the original animations, has plenty of custom animations, and lots of uncommon/rare/super rare animations![br][br]7.2 Changes:[br]Several fixes & improvements.[br]New bathing animations.[br]New whimpering sound.[br]The King Sheep, Pump, does flips,[br]spawns sheep, and disappears now![br][br]Thanks for using![br]You can send feedback to[br]greenstraysheep@gmail.com[br][br]Thank you, Adriano.[br]- Oliver[br][br]Feb. 2, 2020.
